.com/test/sistemi-di-sicurezza-intelligenti-per-la-casa/\">Sistemi di Sicurezza per la Casa</a></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/healthcare.png\",\"id\":346,\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull has-background-dim\"><img class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-346\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/healthcare.png\" data-object-fit=\"cover\"/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Protezione</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Proteggi le persone con soluzioni avanzate: il monitoraggio e la cura della persona sola in casa, è rilevante!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Il monitoraggio&nbsp;costante h24, rileva possibili situazioni anomale. I sensori rilevano le principali attività quotidiane della persona sola, aumentano il comfort abitativo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Il monitoraggio incrementa la sicurezza rilevando e inoltrando allarmi per un aiuto immediato affinché si possa intervenire con l’assistenza necessaria.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/monitoraggio-della-persona/\">Monitoraggio della Persona</a></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\"><!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"id\":95,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large\"><a href=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/sistemi-intelligenti-per-illuminazione/\"><img src=\"http://www.e-polygraphene.com/test/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/smart-lighting1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-95\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/sistemi-intelligenti-per-illuminazione/\">Sistemi Smart per l\'Illuminazione</a></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"id\":348,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large is-style-default\"><a href=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/smart-security/\"><img src=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/electrical-safaty.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-348\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/smart-security/\">Sicurezza Elettrica</a></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/sensirion-general-header-air-pollution-visual-530x400-55db6.jpg\",\"id\":171,\"minHeight\":566,\"minHeightUnit\":\"px\",\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull has-background-dim\" style=\"min-height:566px\"><img class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-171\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/sensirion-general-header-air-pollution-visual-530x400-55db6.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\"/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Disinfezione</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>La qualità dell’aria è un parametro di quanto l’aria sia esente da inquinamento atmosferico e se respirata dall’uomo, sia innocua.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Le soluzioni innovative con sensori wireless dedicati, permettono di monitorare la qualità dell’aria e utilizzare dispositivi che sanificano gli ambienti con modalità diverse, in base a valori acquisiti dagli stessi sensori, attraverso un report dettagliato.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/controllo-della-qualita-dellaria/\">Controllo della Qualità dell\'Aria</a></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https://e-polygraphene.com/test/progetti/\"><strong>Scopri tutti i nostri progetti</strong></a></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->', 'Connessioni Tecnologiche <br> & <br>Sviluppo Software', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-07-19 13:01:33', '2021-07-19 11:01:33', '', 11, 'https://e-polygraphene.com/test/?p=364', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
